Text: The comic featured contributions from some of comics history?s most well-known creators: Alex Toth, Joe Orlando (EC artist and editor), Mike Sekowsky (Justice League artist), Frank Thorne, Jos?-Luis Garc?a-Lopez, Arnold Drake, Len Wein (creator of Swamp Thing and Wolverine), Al Williamson, Jerry Robinson (creator of The Joker), Dan Spiegle, and many others.
